item.title: Viktor Hovland shoots 66 for 6-shot lead at Tour Championship to close in on FedEx Cup title
item.description: ATLANTA (AP) — Viktor Hovland can't remember playing this well with every aspect of his game, and he can't think of a better time for it to all come together. One more round of that and he'll have $18 million to show for it, along with his name on the FedEx Cup trophy.
item.dc:creator: DOUG FERGUSON, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC
